{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/gt2-06132023102228.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-06-13T11:39:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-06-13T12:07:37-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u6e56\u5317\u7f8e\u672f\u5b66\u9662\u5b66\u751f\u88c5\u7f6e\u827a\u672f\u5c55\u54c1\u88ab\u7981\u3000\u53ea\u56e0\u4e8b\u5148\u672a\u83b7\u6279\u51c6", "description": "\u6e56\u5317\u7f8e\u672f\u5b66\u9662\u7684\u5b66\u751f\u65e5\u524d\u5728\u6821\u56ed\u5185\u5c55\u793a\u6709\u5173\u63a2\u8ba8\u523b\u677f\u5370\u8c61\u7684\u88c5\u7f6e\u827a\u672f\u4f5c\u54c1\uff0c\u6821\u65b9\u4fdd\u5b89\u4eba\u5458\u4ee5\u5c55\u54c1\"\u6ca1\u6709\u7ecf\u8fc7\u5ba1\u6279\"\u4e3a\u7531\u52a0\u4ee5\u963b\u6320\u5e76\u62c6\u9664\u5c55\u54c1\u3002", "videos": [], "audios": ["https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/gt2-06132023102228.html/@@stream"], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/gt2-06132023102228.html/@@images/e23a4c1d-1d25-4160-a967-dd4f3c8ffd19.jpeg\"/>\n\u6e56\u5317\u7f8e\u672f\u5b66\u9662\u5b66\u751f\u5c55\u793a\u7684\u88c5\u7f6e\u827a\u672f\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/meiti/gt2-06132023102228.html/@@images/image\">\n <img src=\"https://www.rfa.org//++plone++rfa-resources/img/icon-zoom.png\"/>\n</a>\n\u7f51\u7edc\u622a\u56fe/\u53e4\u4ead\u63d0\u4f9b\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"\\u6e56\\u5317\\u7f8e\\u672f\\u5b66\\u9662\\u5b66\\u751f\\u88c5\\u7f6e\\u827a\\u672f\\u5c55\\u54c1\\u88ab\\u7981\\u3000\\u53ea\\u56e0\\u4e8b\\u5148\\u672a\\u83b7\\u6279\\u51c6\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n                    \"article_uid\